# # rules manifest
ArtifactOwnershipRules | ArtifactOwnershipRules.md | ownership conflict intersection owns validate plan | Artifact ownership is exclusive — only one spec may own a given shared artifact; reads are unrestricted.
SpecIdNamingRules | SpecIdNamingRules.md | spec-id naming slug NNN scaffold branch | Spec IDs must be NNN-slug; generated by incrementing the highest existing prefix.
ChangelogAppendOnlyRule | ChangelogAppendOnlyRule.md | changelog append-only audit cross-artifact mutation relic write | changelog.md is append-only; entries only on cross-artifact mutations via relic write --changelog.
SpecFilesAllowlistRule | SpecFilesAllowlistRule.md | spec files allowlist validate illegal | Only spec.md, plan.md, tasks.md, and artifacts.json are permitted in a spec directory.
ArtifactPathPrefixRule | ArtifactPathPrefixRule.md | artifact path prefix shared validate owns reads | All owns/reads paths in artifacts.json must start with shared/.
TestingRules | TestingRules.md | test bun unit integration temp-dir colocated testing | Test file location, temp-dir pattern, and no-mock-fs rule for all specs adding tests.
